  "texts": [
    "OpenAI does not use data submitted via the API for training purposes, and retains it for only 30 days to comply with regulatory requirements [13].",
    "Using the GPT3.5-Turbo model, the cost per query is less than one Canadian cent (< $0.01 CAD).",
    "Overall, this model is cost-effective and throughout the term cost less than $20 for nearly 3000 separate queries.",
    "Adjusting RAG for performanceWhen working with a RAG system there are three major parameters that can be adjusted to alter the performance of the overall system: the size of the document chunks, the embedding neural network, and the number of chunks retrieved for a given query.",
    "However, it is first important to discuss what \"performance\" means in this context."
